WorkItem.Description:
It seems there is some incompatibility between Rawr 2.1.3 and Character Profiler. For some reason it is ignoring some of my characters. I tried to force it by deleting the CharacterProfiler.lua file and recreating it with information from only one of the characters that Rawr was ignoring/missing and then I got the following error:
 
Error reading saved variable file: InvalidArgument=Value of  '0' is not valid for 'SelectedIndex'.
Parameter name: SelectedIndex
 
I'm using rpgo-CharacterProfiler released on 2008/11/01
I had to import the information using Rawr 2.1.2 and then save it as a Rawr file and open it with 2.1.3
